name: mega_cross_set_mutation_inside_if_then_list_count
section: codegen-cross-layer-stress
args: p:Bool a:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: if branches with mutating set operations must produce expected membership.
law: (= (with [s (set)] (do (if {p} (conj! s {a}) (disj! s {a})) (contains? s {a}))) {p})
